  <h1>About TalkFlip</h1>
  <p class="lead">A random question card game for friends, couples, and hangouts.</p>

  <p>TalkFlip is a conversation card game you start instantly from a single link — no install needed. Break an awkward silence at a gathering, or get to know friends and partners better by flipping cards one at a time and answering or voting. Every prompt is light and answerable in about three seconds.</p>

  <h2>How you play</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Who's Most Likely</b> — everyone points to one person for a prompt.</li>
    <li><b>This or That</b> — pick A or B and say why.</li>
    <li><b>Classic Flip</b> — take turns answering questions.</li>
    <li><b>Hot Seat</b> — questions focus on one person at a time.</li>
    <li><b>Taboo Round</b> — describe a topic while avoiding banned words.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Decks (themes)</h2>
  <p>Pick a deck that fits the mood — Warm Up, Funny, Deep, Couple, Party, or Spicy.</p>

  <h2>Kept safe</h2>
  <p>Sensitive or uncomfortable topics (appearance, income, politics, religion, etc.) are excluded from the core cards. TalkFlip aims for light, fun conversation.</p>

